00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:52.410
Of course, it's
also an ad for them.

00:02:52.410 --> 00:02:54.120
Ad inception.

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:56.020
In the end, we share
ads for the same reason

00:02:56.020 --> 00:02:57.230
that we're going to
share anything else--

00:02:57.230 --> 00:02:59.320
when it comes down to it,
we're celebrating the art.

00:02:59.320 --> 00:03:00.350
We want to know
what you guys think.

00:03:00.350 --> 00:03:02.070
Does it bother you to
share a commercial?

00:03:02.070 --> 00:03:02.940
Let us know in the comments.

